title: Deh Mohammad Hoseyn
text: Deh Mohammad Hoseyn (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Deh Moḥammad Hoseyn) is a village in <a href="Zaz-e%20Sharqi%20Rural%20District">Zaz-e Sharqi Rural District</a>, <a href="Zaz%20va%20Mahru%20District">Zaz va Mahru District</a>, <a href="Aligudarz%20County">Aligudarz County</a>, <a href="Lorestan%20Province">Lorestan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 22, in 5 families.
